flowRoot.flowPara: Figure S8. Phylogeny of LAR and other PIP-family enzymes across land-plant lineages. The phylogenetic tree is computed as in Figure 8. Sequences included are from transcripts from the 1KP project (Ka-Shu Wong et al.,2019). Gene models from annotated genomes are indicated by green checkmarks and sequences compared in Figure S7 are indicated by red stars. Branch support is in % SH-aLRT after 2000 bootstraps.
